column5: hi new to the board anyone no if bronte is fishable today

Hello there and welcome to the board.  Give us a little info about yourself, just a short intro, be sure to include why you love the sport.  You may have better luck in getting the advice you seek  Cant say about Bronte, but I can tell you water levels in the Credit are higher.
I use this site all the time for checking water levels  http://scitech.pyr.ec.gc.ca/waterweb/formnav.asp  Good luck.
